Rake			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.AttackOption	VISIBLE:YES																				DESC:You gain extra natural attack under certain conditions, typically when you grapple your foe. In addition to the options available to all grapplers, you gain two additional claw attacks that you can use only against a grappled foe. YOu must begin your turn grappling to use your rake - you can't begin a grapple and rake in the same turn.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.X
